                <h1>How to Temporarily Pause Life360 Location Sharing</h1>
                <p>To pause Life360, open the app on your device. Navigate to the 'Settings' section and select 'Location Sharing.' Then, toggle off the location sharing feature. This will temporarily suspend location updates to your Circle. Remember, this feature can be useful for privacy, and you can resume sharing anytime by following the same steps.</p>
